Hungary Readies Budget Drafts With Forint Scenarios, Hvg.hu Says

-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 
2011-09-27T16:19:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/hungary-readies-budget-drafts-with-forint-scenarios-hvg-hu-says.html
Hungary’s government is preparing
three separate drafts for the 2012 budget based on different
scenarios for the forint’s exchange rate versus the euro,
including as weak as 300,  hvg.hu  reported.  The Cabinet is calculating the budget with exchange rates
at 260, 280 and 300, respectively, the news portal reported,
citing information from a meeting of ruling party lawmakers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest at 
 agergely@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  